---
import PageLayout from "@/layouts/PageLayout.astro";
---

<PageLayout
  title="let's chat | oscarama"
  description="I'd love to meet you. Let's grab coffee or hop on a call."
  ogUrl="https://oscarama.dev/chat"
>
  <a class="text-sm text-white/50 hover:text-white/70 transition-colors" href="/">
    &larr; back home
  </a>

  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-8">let's chat</h1>

  <div class="flex flex-col mt-8">
    <p class="text-lg text-white/90">
      in 2026 I'm on a mission to meet as many interesting people as possible.
    </p>
    <p class="text-sm text-white/70 mt-4">
      whether you're building something cool, exploring a wild idea, or just want to talk about
      rockets and climbing walls - I'm always down for a good conversation.
    </p>
  </div>

  <a
    class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-full sm:w-fit mt-10 px-8 py-4 bg-[#E56717] text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-[#c9550f] transition-colors duration-200"
    href="https://cal.oscarama.dev"
    onclick="window.posthog?.capture('lets_chat_clicked', { source: 'chat_page' })"
  >
    book a time to chat
  </a>

  <p class="text-sm text-white/70 mt-10">
    this is a convenient way to do it, but I'd honestly rather you just DM me :p<br />{" "}
    <a
      href="https://x.com/oscarfalll"
      target="_blank"
      class="text-[#E56717] hover:underline"
      onclick="window.posthog?.capture('social_link_clicked', { platform: 'X', source: 'chat_page' })"
      >Twitter</a
    >{" "}
    or{" "}
    <a
      href="https://linkedin.com/in/oscarfalemara"
      target="_blank"
      class="text-[#E56717] hover:underline"
      onclick="window.posthog?.capture('social_link_clicked', { platform: 'LinkedIn', source: 'chat_page' })"
      >LinkedIn</a
    > - DMs are always open. or if I know you, then WhatsApp is best :)
  </p>
  <p class="text-sm text-white/70 mt-6">
    I also run events in London - <a
      href="/events"
      target="_blank"
      class="text-[#E56717] hover:underline">sign up</a
    > to one!
  </p>

  <div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-white/10">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">how it works</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-6">
      <div class="flex flex-col">
        <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#E56717]">01</span>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold mt-2">pick a time</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-white/60 mt-1">choose a time slot that works for you</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col">
        <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#E56717]">02</span>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold mt-2">choose the format</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-white/60 mt-1">coffee in London or video call from anywhere</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col">
        <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#E56717]">03</span>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold mt-2">let's talk</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-white/60 mt-1">no agenda needed - just good conversation</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-white/10">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">things I love talking about</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-x-8 gap-y-4 mt-6">
      <div class="flex flex-col">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">aerospace</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-white/60">
          rockets, drones, satellites - how they fly, how they're built, and the future of space
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">AI & agents</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-white/60">
          AGI timelines, fine-tuning, architecture, and actually useful applications
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">embedded systems</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-white/60">
          microcontrollers, RTOS, signal processing - the stuff that makes hardware tick
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">the outdoors</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-white/60">
          mountaineering, bouldering, ultralight hiking - bonus points if you have beta
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">blockchain & crypto</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-white/60">
          ZK proofs, token economics, actual real-world payment use cases
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">everything else</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-white/60">
          quantum physics, nuclear fusion, neuroscience, or whatever you're excited about
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</PageLayout>
